<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome | AutoParts Pro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/product-list.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --main-white: #ffffff;
            --main-black: #000000;
            --main-orange: #ff6600;
            --light-grey: #f9f9f9;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--main-white);
            color: var(--main-black);
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Hero Section - White background with black text */
        .hero {
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--main-white);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: var(--main-black);
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 900;
            border: none; /* Resetting the border from product-list.css */
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: var(--main-orange);
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background-color: var(--main-white);
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--main-black);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Small orange underline for the title */
        .about-section h2::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 5px;
            background-color: var(--main-orange);
            margin: 10px auto;
        }

        .about-content {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .about-content strong {
            color: var(--main-black);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--main-orange);
        }

        /* Button - Black & Orange */
        .btn-cta {
            background-color: var(--main-black);
            color: var(--main-white);
            padding: 20px 45px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border: 2px solid var(--main-black);
            transition: 0.3s all ease;
        }

        .btn-cta:hover {
            background-color: var(--main-orange);
            border-color: var(--main-orange);
            color: var(--main-black);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* Partnership highlights */
        .partners {
            margin-top: 60px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #999;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .partners span {
            color: var(--main-orange);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
               <img src="/images/logo1.jpg" width="100px">

        <h1>Auto Spare Parts</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>GEAR <span>UP.</span></h1>
        <p>Your journey deserves the best components.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container-main">
        <section class="about-section">
            <div class="about-container">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p class="about-content">
                    At Auto Spare Parts, we specialize in the <strong>full availability</strong> of high-performance automotive pieces. 
                    From specialized engine units to everyday maintenance parts, we ensure that you never have to wait for the components you need. 
                    Our strength lies in our network of <strong>multiple international cooperators</strong>, allowing us to source and 
                    distribute parts with unmatched speed and reliability. No matter the make or model, our pieces are tested 
                    to withstand the toughest road conditions.
                </p>

                <a href="/products" class="btn-cta">Explore All Pieces</a>

                <div class="partners">
                    <div><span>●</span> Premium Quality</div>
                    <div><span>●</span> Global Network</div>
                    <div><span>●</span> Direct Sourcing</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>